===Etymology===

From {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|tangentem|lang=la}}, the accusative of {{term|tangens|tangēns|touching|lang=la}} the [[present participle]] of the verb {{term|tango|tangō|to touch|lang=la}}. From the the phrase {{term||[[linea#Latin|līnea]] [[tango#Latin|tangēns]]|a touching line}}.

